{"tid":1478573,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"817派傳單 做818民宣","createTime":"2019-08-16T14:42:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T03:35:09.000Z","uid":266130,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"465786dda3c3eaad83691a3754779c28e6c52465","tid":1478573,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:42:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><em>好重要嘅文宣</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n好記得615個日 好多市民自發派傳單 幫616做勢<span style=\"color: brown;\">依種落區宣傳嘅方法 好做到勢</span><br />\n記得個日銅鑼灣同旺角基本上每個路口都有人派<span style=\"color: orange;\">甘樣令到和理非知道佢地好有需要走出來<br />\n令佢地知道件事好迫切 唔可以置身事外</span><br />\n加上黎緊818變集會 好多和理非真心驚行出馬路會變非法集結 然後警犬清場 會變衝動 <br />\n所以可能會嚇走好多一家大細 818會少左人<br />\n所以我地一定要落區做好民宣<br />\n<br />\n所以想問聽日817有冇人出黎派傳單<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去嘅留低你會幾點去邊區派</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">比其他手足知道多人缺人 可以補位</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n冇凖備可以去print民陣fb share嗰張<br />\n有心可以自己整<br />\nPoster內容重點係 *當初二百萬人為守護香港走出黎 黎到依刻我地要為守護人性良知而走出黎*<br />\n 重要強調*一個都不能少* *唔可以恐懼*"},{"pid":"7134c5fe148647334fd5056d4c1ed65db5aee5c7","tid":1478573,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"8f4ddc608d406dd5047e9da29813b3c9cbfa5441","tid":1478573,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:43:52.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7800e679c1aa1a9f81d86fa027d33fbd30d99f49","tid":1478573,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:44:30.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"375115f8b5749b38043c0df0104b58fc3776d7ea","tid":1478573,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T14:44:40.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"89fe11935415a3ede71d88ca1a65255a3108d28e","tid":1478573,"uid":266130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":